claim.claim-text:
1. A method, comprising:
providing a tissue having desired cells that are less prone to destructive freezing and undesired cells that are more prone to destructive freezing, infusing the desired cells with a cryoprotectant solution comprising a cryoprotective agent, and infusing the undesired cells with solution that does not contain the cryoprotective agent;
freezing the tissue;
disrupting the tissue;
warming the tissue; and
separating the desired cells from undesired cellular material to obtain a product.
